{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu dohd inan arri tahs\npreekſchturramas Bruunas ta-\nivas Peſtſchanas / un tu manni\npaseinodams eſſi maun augſtu\npadarriſs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi mannamSohtam\nplattu Weetu appaſſch man dar-\nrijs / ka manni Krumſti ne irr\nflihdeiſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es dſihſchohs mannam\nGenaidneekam pakkat / un pa-\nnahktchu tohs / un ne atgreeſt-\nschohs / pirms es tohs buhſchu\nisdeldejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es isdeldeſchu tohs / un\nfadauſischu tohs/ ka tee ne war-\nrehs zeltees/teem jahriht appaſſch\nmannahm Kahjahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tu apjohti mann ar\nSpehſnu us Katru / tu nolohzi\nappaſſch man/ kas prett maun\nzelkahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu leezi mannuß Genaid-\nneekus preekſch mannim behgt /\nun mannuß Nihdetajus isnihzt-\nnaju es.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee usluhkojahs/ bet Pe-\nſtitaja newaid / us to KUNGU/\nbet wiꞥſch teem ne atbildeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es ſagruhdifchu tohs fa\nSemmes Pihſchlus / es famih-\nfchu un iſkaifichu tohs/ fa Dub-\nkus us Gelahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi mann no mannu\nLaufchu Kiſdahm iſglahbis / tu\neſſi mann var Galwu lizzisteem\nPagaſſeem: Landis/ fo es ne pa-\nſinn/ man kalpo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Swefchi Behrni irr\nman par Melluteem tappuſch\nkad winnu Auſß dsirdeja/ irr\nmann paklaufigi tappuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schwefchi Behrni irr\nnihkuſchi/ un gohrahs eeſch\nwahm Pillim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS dſihu\nun flatwehts irr mans Patr\nruins / un augſti flatwehts\nDeews/ tas Patwerungs mani\nPeſtſchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas STIPRAI\nDEEWS/ kas man Atre-\nſchanas dohd/ un Laudis\npakſch mannim nomett.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas mann iſwadda\nmanneemi Genaidneekem : Un\npa-augſtina mann pabr tee\nkas prett man zeltahs / no te\nWarras-Darritajeem iſglahb\nmann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 50,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz flatweſchu es\nKUNgs ſtarp teem Paganee\nun dseedafchu tawam Wa-\ndam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch irr weens Pe-\nſchanas Turnis jawaim Re-\nxam / un darra labbi taw\nSwaiditam Dabwidam / winna Dsimmmam muhſch\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
